    <h1>Canonical URL</h1>
    <p class="description">The HTML tag that tells Google the preferred version of a page when the same or near-duplicate content is reachable through multiple URLs. Consolidates ranking signals to <strong>one authoritative URL</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
